The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 Iraq bomber

 Falluja, May 3 (Reuters): A suicide bomber blew himself up among a crowd of men waiting to sign up to join the police force in Falluja today, killing at least 18 people.

 Most of the 20 people wounded in the attack on the police recruits were in a critical condition. large crowds drawn to recruiting centres are a common target. 




